## React + Tailwind → React Native Component Conversion

Convert this React + Tailwind TypeScript component into React Native TypeScript.

**RULES:**
- Replace all HTML elements with React Native equivalents
- Convert Tailwind classes into `StyleSheet` styles manually
- Keep layout visually identical
- Preserve spacing scale exactly
- Convert flex utilities properly
- Remove `hover:`, `focus:`, `group-`, and other web-only utilities
- Convert responsive classes (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`) into `Dimensions`-based logic if needed
- Keep TypeScript types
- Output only valid React Native code

