## Practical Notes / Warnings

- If CSS Grid is used, manual layout adjustments in flexbox will be required.
- For complex animations, plan to use `react-native-reanimated`.
- If UI libraries like MUI / Ant Design are used, those components must be rewritten with React Native primitives or a compatible UI library.
- A 100% automatic conversion is not realistic, but these prompts should accelerate the process by roughly 70–85%.

